# Ruwan_EVM
Project of design and implementation of EVM (Electronic Voting Machine) using Microcontroller.

Hello all! This is to build up EVM, using Microcontrollers, simple design as an Embedded system.
Users can vote in digital manner, which is highly effective, as an low cost product.
Modules are distributed among you dividing basic parts.
4-bit Adder and 4by1 Mux modules are created.
